{"tid":925944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恒安邨單位傳異味　消防破門揭男子燒炭亡","createTime":"2018-12-03T05:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T06:18:06.000Z","uid":160807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a25c51c53da0ea92541482562b97ce273b1b404e","tid":925944,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T05:38:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181202/photo/bkn-20181202143757743-1202_00822_001_01b.jpg?20181202173851\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181202%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181202143757743-1202_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20181202173851&h=0edb8a79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山恒安邨男子燒炭亡。今日(2日)下午2時02分，一名姓蕭(40歲)男子到恆安邨恆星樓一單位探望姓羅(38歲)表弟時，發現單位傳出異味，惟拍門無人應，擔心屋內有事故發生，遂報警求助。消防接報到場破門入屋，揭發羅在屋內燒炭死亡，旁邊有一盤燃燼的炭。警方在場調查，檢獲遺書，初步相信事件無可疑，事主死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=skePNZIMzG5atM%2FMZUr7wp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=60944149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181202/bkn-20181202143757743-1202_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181202%2Fbkn-20181202143757743-1202_00822_001.html&d=skePNZIMzG5atM%2FMZUr7wp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=b9bc937d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181202/bkn-20181202143757743-1202_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"36e2dbfc3fb1712b9c3b280cb78ec1f64eb7046d","tid":925944,"uid":210851,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T06:07:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c6d066aa0e0ac8b0c3b17ba7dbba4bb